  "description": "Built Wellframe's Dashboard as a Plinth deep-ink \"Daily Briefing Console\" at /: a readiness dial, overnight vitals telemetry, an observant single-message coach transmission, and yesterday's field log, plus a ⌘K coach-dock stub and the day-one onboarding empty state (production starts empty). Backed by Prisma/SQLite (DailyBriefing, Vital, Workout) with per-scenario seeds; extracted pure helpers (emphasize, clampPct, dial geometry) under unit test. Covered by 19 tests and 23 scenarios (18 component + 5 application: empty / primed / low-readiness / partial-data / no-workout).",
